title: 插件Very Dangerous Nether进入地狱报错
author: Cheris
txt_content:
本帖最后由 Cheris 于 2020-8-10 12:20 编辑 

[12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum] [Yum 事件监控] 插件 VeryDangerousNether 处理 CreatureSpawnEvent 事件时发生异常! [12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum] 异常名称: java.lang.NoSuchFieldError [12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum] 异常说明: NETHER_WASTES [12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum] 简易错误信息如下: [12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum]     位于 verydangerousnether.verydangerousnether.nether.mobs.SpawnHandler.spawnMobs(SpawnHandler.java:32) [12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum]     位于 com.destroystokyo.paper.event.executor.asm.generated.GeneratedEventExecutor63.execute(未知:-1) [12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum]     位于 org.bukkit.plugin.EventExecutor.lambda$create$1(EventExecutor.java:69) [12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum]     位于 co.aikar.timings.TimedEventExecutor.execute(TimedEventExecutor.java:80) [12:09:53] [Server thread/INFO]: [Yum]     位于 pw.yumc.Yum.inject.ListenerInjector.execute(ListenerInjector.java:88)
服务端1.15.2paper,这个报错是只有玩家进入地狱才会出现，插件的前置libsdisguises，protocollib都安了
Very Dangerous Nether这个插件有个地狱刷插件自定义生物的功能，我开启和关闭都是一样的报错
